<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/seal.png" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>about — grissobel</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script is:inline src="https://code.iconify.design/3/3.1.1/iconify.min.js"></script>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        background: #fff;
        font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
        color: #2a2d3a;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }

      header {
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 600px;
        padding: 2rem 0 0 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }

      a.seal-home {
        display: inline-block;
      }

      a.seal-home img {
        width: 100px;
        opacity: 0.85;
      }

      a.seal-home img:hover {
        opacity: 1;
      }

      .back {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        opacity: 0.5;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #2a2d3a;
        align-self: flex-start;
      }

      .back:hover {
        opacity: 1;
      }

      .header-rule {
        width: 100%;
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #c8cad4;
      }

      main {
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 600px;
        padding: 3rem 0 4rem 0;
        flex: 1;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.6rem;
        font-weight: 300;
        letter-spacing: 0.4em;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
      }

      hr {
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #c8cad4;
        margin: 2.5rem 0;
      }

      .photo-block {
        display: flex;
        gap: 2.5rem;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .avatar {
        width: 140px;
        height: 140px;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 50%;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        filter: grayscale(20%);
        opacity: 1;
      }

      .bio {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .bio p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.75;
        opacity: 0.85;
      }

      .inline-link {
        color: #2a2d3a;
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-underline-offset: 3px;
        opacity: 0.7;
      }

      .inline-link:hover {
        opacity: 1;
      }

      footer {
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 600px;
        padding: 2rem 0;
        font-size: 1rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        color: #2a2d3a;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        border-top: 1px solid #c8cad4;
      }

      footer p {
        margin: 0;
      }

      .icons {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .icons a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #2a2d3a;
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        opacity: 0.6;
      }

      .icons a:hover {
        opacity: 1;
      }

      @media (max-width: 500px) {
        .photo-block {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
          text-align: center;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <a href="/" class="back">← grissobel</a>
      <a href="/" class="seal-home">
        <img src="/seal.png" alt="grissobel" />
      </a>
      <hr class="header-rule" />
    </header>

    <main>
      <h1>about</h1>

      <section>
        <div class="photo-block">
          <img src="/about_avatar.JPG" alt="gris" class="avatar" />
          <div class="bio">
            <p>Hi, I'm Gris. I'm a writer, engineer, and mother. I build software and hardware, write essays about what I'm learning, and maintain a few projects I'm passionate about.</p>
            <p>As both a software and electrical engineer, I combine my knowledge of both disciplines to make fun things or solve everyday problems — my way.</p>
            <p>My writing lives on Substack in <em>grey matters</em>, where I publish weekly essays and occasional curations of children's books (<em>tiny stacks</em>) about motherhood, cooking, books, fly fishing, and whatever else has been on my mind.</p>
            <p>This site routes you to my work. Substack takes you to my essays. Engineering shows my software and hardware work.</p>
            <p>You can reach me via <a href="mailto:hello@grissobel.com" class="inline-link">email</a>, or find me on <a href="https://grissobel.substack.com" target="_blank" class="inline-link">Substack</a>, <a href="https://github.com/grissobel" target="_blank" class="inline-link">GitHub</a>, <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" class="inline-link">Instagram</a>, <a href="https://goodreads.com" target="_blank" class="inline-link">Goodreads</a>, and <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" class="inline-link">LinkedIn</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <p>© 2026 grissobel</p>
      <div class="icons">
        <a href="/search" aria-label="search"><span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:magnify"></span></a>
        <a href="https://grissobel.substack.com" target="_blank" aria-label="substack"><span class="iconify" data-icon="simple-icons:substack"></span></a>
        <a href="https://instagram.com/grissobel" target="_blank" aria-label="instagram"><span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:instagram"></span></a>
        <a href="https://github.com/grissobel" target="_blank" aria-label="github"><span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:github"></span></a>
        <a href="https://goodreads.com/grissobel" target="_blank" aria-label="goodreads"><span class="iconify" data-icon="simple-icons:goodreads"></span></a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/grissobel" target="_blank" aria-label="linkedin"><span class="iconify" data-icon="mdi:linkedin"></span></a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>